dct_title_s: Paskaerte van de Zuy¨dt en Noordt Revier in Nieu Nederlant (Copy 2)
dct_description_sm: Depths shown by soundings. "In effect this map is the first of present day New Jersey and is the most detailed map of the region to date."--Burden, P.D. The mapping of North America, p. 495. Imprint from Burden. From: De zee-atlas ofte water-wereld / Pieter Goos. Amsterdam: Pieter Goos, 1666.
